\s Ilizwi lemukelwa ngabezizwe liphikwa ngamaJuda
\p
\v 42 Kwathi ekuphumeni kwamaJuda esinagogeni\x + 13.16.\x*, abezizwe bacela ukuthi lamazwi akhulunywe kubo ngesabatha elilandelayo\x + 13.44.\x*.
